##Overview

[REGION:fullwidth]
![](AnimationGraph.png)
[/REGION]

The **Graph Mode** of **Persona** is where you specify the logic behind and hook up animations and animation states based off variables and conditions set within the **AnimGraph** and **EventGraph**. Working with the graphs, is similar to working with **Blueprint** graphs however there are some key details to **Animation Blueprints** as outlined below. 

##Animation Blueprints Overview

[INCLUDE:Engine/Animation/AnimBlueprints#Intro]

For more information on working with **Animation Blueprints**, refer to the [Animation Blueprints](Engine/Animation/AnimBlueprints) documentation. 




